    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1740&q=80',
      alt: 'About Us',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-4">
        Built for the Future of Cloud Operations
      </h3>
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-muted mb-4">
        We're not just another cloud services company. We're infrastructure partners.
      </p>

      <p class="text-muted mb-4">We started with a simple belief:</p>

      <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-4 italic text-lg text-muted mb-6">
        Infrastructure shouldn't be manual, expensive, or unreliable.<br />
        It should be automated. Scalable. Effortless.
      </blockquote>

      <p class="text-muted mb-6">
        So we built cloud and operations services that transform infrastructure â€” powered by <span class="font-semibold"
          >cloud-native technologies</span
        > and best practices that ensure reliable, scalable operations.
      </p>

      <h4 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white mb-3">ðŸŒŸ Our Vision</h4>
      <p class="text-muted mb-4">
        To create a world where <span class="font-semibold">infrastructure runs itself</span> â€” so teams can focus on
        building great products.
      </p>

      <h4 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white mb-3">ðŸŽ¯ Our Mission</h4>
      <p class="text-muted">
        To revolutionize cloud operations by merging automation, scalability, reliability, and cost optimization. We empower
        <span class="font-semibold">startups</span>, <span class="font-semibold">growing businesses</span>, and <span
          class="font-semibold"
          >enterprises</span
        > to operate with <span class="font-semibold">world-class cloud infrastructure</span>.
      </p>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

  <!-- CallToAction Widget *********** -->

